summary: 该插件用于检测Dedecms系统中的多个漏洞，包括CVE-2018-7700远程命令执行漏洞、membergroup SQL注入漏洞以及CVE-2018-6910信息泄露漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect multiple vulnerabilities in the Dedecms system, including CVE-2018-7700 remote command execution vulnerability, membergroup SQL injection vulnerability, and CVE-2018-6910 information disclosure vulnerability.
